|corange--- PHASE 2 ---
Bomb players move to markers, tank soak with the big bomb
Dodge the lines on the ground

|corange--- PHASE 3 ---
{tank} Take add with 1 weapon away from other adds
{tank} Stack adds with 2 weapons on casters for cleave
Interupt Cosmic Beacon, ignore Starblast

|corange--- PHASE 4 ---
{tank} Don't bother tank swapping, just survive as long as possible
{healer} Heal the tree to keep the free revives up longer

Bomb players move out, tanks don't stack with big bomb for this phase
Kills adds ASAP
Dead people collect orbs before moving to the tree for a rez